data.description: PRICE REDUCED OVER $100,000.00 OUR LOSS COULD BE YOUR GAIN. Back on market no fault of sellers…An entertainer's dream come true, this property features a spacious open floor plan and stunning outdoor space !  The gourmet kitchen is big enough to host all of the family for the holidays. This  brick front beauty is guaranteed to check all the boxes! It is  peacefully situated on 3 acres on a  cul-de-sac lot in the highly sought after Glen Haven Estates in Sotsylvania County. This home offers privacy & convenience while boasting over 6,600 square feet of living space and an incredible entertainer's dream rear yard with saltwater pool. The inviting two-story foyer opens to the elegant living room and formal dining room with butlers pantry. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight with expansive counter space, large pantry, eating area and windows galore!. Two-story family room featuring two sided gas fireplace that opens to the sunroom surrounded by windows.  The upper level features Master suite with coffered ceiling, two walk-in closets & spa like bathroom with shower, soaking tub & his and her vanities three additional bedrooms and two additional  bathrooms. The lower level offers a large recreation room, full bathroom, media room,5th bedroom, gym/art/6th bedroom not to code and  storage. The outdoor living space includes a large patio with outdoor bar with granite counter tops, drive way to accommodate large family gatherings, room to build detached garage and so much more. Bring the family and see what Macintyre court has to offer!
